Summary: An unusual object hovering over my lady friend and I.
divs: Sighting DetailsMy lady friend and I were walking home from somewhere. When we were close to her apartment by the preschool I felt like somebody was watching me. So I looked up, and I saw right above my head about 20 yards high a round 6 foot in diameter object. As soon as I saw it it disappeared into space at a high speed. It was very beautiful having colors of orange, pink, blue and violet. Later I found out my lady friend saw it long before I did, but did not say anything. Thank you.
